Cell["\<\
You can vary the probability of the transition from 2 to 1 with the slider. \
Because the sum of the probabilities is 1, for each state's total \
transitions, the transition probability for the transition from 2 to 3 is \
internally computed to sum to 1 when you drag the slider.\
\>", "Text"],

